{"tid":740500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"非法靠近VIP包廂 中國球迷看世界盃遭罰","createTime":"2018-07-13T02:31:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-13T03:11:03.000Z","uid":39464,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93b0eae8524604e98084158e50a3eeecc0bfd1ac","tid":740500,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/103114_c889c63048aa448c6a391a26536a2542.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F103114_c889c63048aa448c6a391a26536a2542.png&h=98e492b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2018俄羅斯世界盃足球賽只剩2場賽事，中國足球隊雖未打進本屆賽事，但靠著大量廣告和球迷，在世足賽狂刷存在感，但近日卻傳出非法事件，有中國球迷試圖非法靠近VIP包廂，遭俄國法院開罰。<br />\n<br />\n《俄羅斯衛星通訊社》報導，俄國聖彼得堡市法院聯合新聞處表示，一名持有球票座位在角球區的中國球迷，在10日舉行的法國對比利時的準決賽期間，進入中央觀眾區，試圖非法靠近VIP包廂。<br />\n<br />\n比賽期間，法國總統馬克宏（Emmanuel Macron）、比利時國王菲利普（King Philippe）和王后瑪蒂爾德（Queen Mathilde），以及國際足球總會會長因凡蒂諾（Gianni Infantino），正在該包廂內觀賽。<br />\n<br />\n俄國世足賽規定，觀者得對號入座，不可闖入其他座席區域。該中國公民因違法行政違規，遭聖彼得堡地區法院判處3000盧布（約1500新台幣）罰款，並禁止在6個月內到現場觀看正式體育賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2486830\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2486830&d=3NWyfr1RrCcTnPgagDBXZEkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ef2c8bcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2486830&h=77510928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2486830</a>"},{"pid":"068be57b1b492851505d2d27bc2b1818261c7113","tid":740500,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:33:23.000Z","msg":"抵死<br />\n罰錢事小 應坐埋監"},{"pid":"2dcb10921baab2cc8736350bbe6b42d9700613b7","tid":740500,"uid":79145,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:44:23.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無中國份都要扯晒旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2441b31f9275134611facc85fa434083cfb218f9","tid":740500,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"唔夠戰鬥民族打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca80efa464b5e78fe8ce3103204d03d1f7c2aac6","tid":740500,"uid":156652,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:49:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/13/104911_161b72947116f96067d28af6ff6939ac.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F13%2F104911_161b72947116f96067d28af6ff6939ac.gif&h=e2ec544a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3a533cc454a75d48415f8b7917aa9329f2a3ca7","tid":740500,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"好肉酸"},{"pid":"544c8def736727e892f492852bd11e4fcf837aba","tid":740500,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T02:52:12.000Z","msg":"中國人真係又柒又無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0116d037b51e5b394a64271cdd80145830f89ba3","tid":740500,"uid":52881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"普京:想偷我雞?"}]}